class  canonMotion
 This class is for the canonical commands STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE, STRAIGHT_FEED, and ARC_FEED. canonMotion is an ABC. Its children should only be instantiated via canonLine::canonLineFactory(), which creates linearMotion objects for STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE and STRAIGHT_FEED commands, and helicalMotion objects for ARC_FEED commands.
